(MEMO METADATA) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(Every memo begins with a standardized header:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    # RFC-NNN: Title) show newline
(    Status: Draft | Proposed | Implemented | Historic) show newline
(    Category: Standards Track | Informational | Experimental | BCP | Historic) show newline
(    Scope: core | federation | local) show newline
(    Created: YYYY-MM-DD) show newline
(    Updated: YYYY-MM-DD) show newline
(    Author: Name <email>) show newline
(    Origin: federation-name | core) show newline
(    Signed: <spki-hash> \(optional\)) show newline
(    Updates: RFC-NNN \(if applicable\)) show newline
(    Obsoletes: RFC-NNN \(if applicable\)) show newline
(    ---) show newline
(    ## Abstract) show newline
(    One paragraph summary.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Required Fields) show newline
(---------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(  Field      Required   Description                ) show newline
(  Status     Yes        Document lifecycle stage   ) show newline
(  Category   Yes        Document type              ) show newline
(  Scope      Yes        Visibility and authority   ) show newline
(  Created    Yes        Initial authorship date    ) show newline
(  Author     Yes        Who penned the memo        ) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Optional Fields) show newline
(---------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(  Field       When Used                     ) show newline
(  Updated     After modifications           ) show newline
(  Origin      For federation-scoped memos   ) show newline
(  Signed      For authenticated memos       ) show newline
(  Updates     When extending prior memo     ) show newline
(  Obsoletes   When replacing prior memo     ) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
(NAMING SCOPE) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(Memos exist at three scopes:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(  Scope        Format           Authority            Visibility          ) show newline
(  core         RFC-NNN          Core maintainers     Global, canonical   ) show newline
(  federation   <fed>:memo-NNN   Federation members   Federation-wide     ) show newline
(  local        local:memo-NNN   Node author          Single node         ) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Core Scope) show newline
(----------) show newline
() show newline
(Core memos use IETF-style sequential numbering:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    Memo-001, Memo-002, ... Memo-043) show newline
() show newline
(These are canonical specifications for the Library of Cyberspace.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Federation Scope) show newline
(----------------) show newline
() show newline
(Federation memos are namespaced by federation identifier:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    yoyodyne:memo-001) show newline
(    alexandria:memo-042) show newline
() show newline
(Each federation maintains its own numbering sequence.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Local Scope) show newline
(-----------) show newline
() show newline
(Local memos exist only on the authoring node:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    local:memo-001) show newline
() show newline
(Local memos are drafts, notes, or node-specific documentation.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
(PROMOTION PATH) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(Memos flow upward through scopes:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    local:memo  ->  fed:memo  ->  RFC) show newline
(        |            |           |) show newline
(      draft     federation    canonical) show newline
(                 review       consensus) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Local to Federation) show newline
(-------------------) show newline
() show newline
(A node author submits a local memo to their federation:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(memo-promote "local:memo-007" 'federation\)) show newline
(    ;; -> yoyodyne:memo-023) show newline
() show newline
(Federation review and rough consensus required.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(Federation to Core) show newline
(------------------) show newline
() show newline
(A federation submits a memo for core adoption:) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    \(memo-promote "yoyodyne:memo-023" 'core\)) show newline
(    ;; -> Memo-044 \(after consensus\)) show newline
() show newline
(Cross-federation review and rough consensus required.) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
