(VERNACULAR) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
(We say:) show newline
() show newline
(  * "Pen a memo" - author a document) show newline
(  * "The memo specifies..." - referring to content) show newline
(  * "Promote the memo" - elevate scope) show newline
(  * "See the RFC" - cite by number) show newline
() show newline
(We don't say:) show newline
() show newline
(  * "Request for comments" - we're not requesting) show newline
(  * "Submit an RFC" - we pen memos, they become RFCs) show newline
() show newline
